    "The frequent mention of certain entities can be interpreted as one sort of framing technique.",
    "We obtain a set of entities from the generation P (Ŷ) and corresponding frequencies, adopting a pre-trained Named Entity Recognition (NER) model.",
    "To conduct comparative analysis across the models, we obtain the set of entities that are frequently mentioned entities of each LLM per topic.",
